n working hard to improve the supply of houses by signing housing accords, by establishing special housing areas, and, also, we are very keen to reform the Resource Management Act. That is why this legislation is important, because this is to extend the Housing Accords and Special Housing Areas Act 2013 so that more special housing areas can be established as appropriate. I support this bill and commend it to the House.</p></div></body>
